title: Putin Rejects Russian Economic Collapse Predictions — Highlights Active BRICS, SCO Cooperation
description: Russian President Vladimir Putin says Russia is actively cooperating with major international organizations, including the BRICS group, the Shanghai Cooperation Organization (SCO), the Association of Southeast Asian Nations (ASEAN), the Gulf Cooperation Council (GCC), and multilateral organizations in Latin America and Africa.
